able to announce a return to the black.
Pre-tax profits for the 12 months to July 30 emerged at Pounds 3.25m,
against losses last time of Pounds 2.09m, on total turnover of Pounds 112m
(Pounds 106m) - Pounds 2.04m was from discontinued activities.
